"tid":428802,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"我鍾意睇粵語長片多過粵劇你又點睇?"},{"pid":"8cfd33f489a692ef49e719cf7ce65d1a6083437e","tid":428802,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家仲有冇睇大戲呢樣野</blockquote><br />\n去新光，私處中心，仲有每年一度球場同一班睇唔見既觀眾一齊睇"},{"pid":"72dd02444b96d183467bedcebf6005ec0e9f3c0b","tid":428802,"uid":76115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意睇粵語長片多過粵劇你又點睇?</blockquote><br />\n粵語長片好多都係文人知識分子寫同拍, 台詞雅正, 講三綱六紀, 傳統道德觀, 上一代人睇得多都正氣啲<br />\n而家啲廢老淨係識睇埋手機啲中共國劇集、viral片, 條條一係講亂倫通奸, 一係講邊個畀人睇唔起最後發左達屌打班仇家, 個腦淨係得屌女同埋幻想用錢撻人, 所以個樣都賊眉賊眼啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d67f792828fc02e9a6b4f64434f0e5fc634ecd7","tid":428802,"uid":11753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"有文化果啲死撚曬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家班老中坑個撚個賊眉賊眼猥猥瑣瑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044bcd950cbf5f668a7d58db1e1b7f143a65c1ba","tid":428802,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有文化果啲死撚曬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家班老中坑個撚個賊眉賊眼猥猥瑣瑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wzyHqji-zug/UWbBb9LHJxI/AAAAAAAAFZM/RLlLODVO-sw/s640/hk-scumbag-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-wzyHqji-zug%2FUWbBb9LHJxI%2FAAAAAAAAFZM%2FRLlLODVO-sw%2Fs640%2Fhk-scumbag-2.jpg&h=66bc562c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"044b02a7ed10bff3e9f218f239e6b5684be88d08","tid":428802,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:24:06.000Z","msg":"舊時老人家係 民國時期走落嚟<br />\n有唔少都受過吓教育<br />\n有文化d好正常"},{"pid":"409843a0e8bbfd3b8fc6f92d429706eac73723eb","tid":428802,"uid":108946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:36:07.000Z","msg":"我最有印象係胭脂扣梅姐開波嗰段南音<br />\n涼風有信 秋月無邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a18c7a8563cf4d792e63d5292c1b3ba588bad8","tid":428802,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:04:15.000Z","msg":"有時鍾意啲垃圾舞嘅廢老廢中可能係比較後期由支那就落嚟班粉腸<br />\n<br />\n嗰班人有啲自出娘胎或者年青嗰陣，就俾文革啲乜柒舞紅歌洗撚晒腦，所以唔聽粵劇都唔出奇，亦唔排除班撚屌鹹濕，想食班北姑嘅<br />\n<br />\n講真正常就算唔聽粵曲，都聽鄭錦昌麗莎，台灣嗰堆國語歌（咩青山尤雅，姚蘇蓉，鄧麗君嗰啲），或者鄭少秋羅文嗰堆啦"},{"pid":"10402514cc7d63583fa4361ffeb4d13aed18d5e5","tid":428802,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家仲有冇睇大戲呢樣野</blockquote><br />\n去新光，<strong>私處中心</strong>，仲有每年一度球場同一班睇唔見既觀眾一齊睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私處嗰度唔係仲起緊，未屌得住咩？"},{"pid":"692fca9f9c17ab21f3470ab9b20d6202d5204810","tid":428802,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:07:02.000Z","msg":"粵曲仲有一一"},{"pid":"64db6fabbcb4e88c70afcfc3efc2604d4a8614a7","tid":428802,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:08:15.000Z","msg":"粵曲仲要有歷史背景故事架喎<br />\n啲大媽書又唔撚讀點會有共鳴"},{"pid":"ae65e8a05eb3149030fc33ad6530529fa35a043f","tid":428802,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:20:07.000Z","msg":"日日引入埋150件垃圾廢老<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47dc18013079a5faffdf2c8bdf928ff2518d3121","tid":428802,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當上一代聽粵典果陣你地有欣賞過咩？</blockquote><br />\n唔識欣賞但點都好睇好聽過大媽舞<br />\n大媽舞係完全冇文化底係入面"},{"pid":"ecc56a8ef9651c81804bf4a4ba96e1a5a35d63a2","tid":428802,"uid":29804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁汪明荃一定係香港文化代表了</blockquote><br />\n唔計佢政治立場<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係撚呀<br />\n屎到仆街 冇料扮四條"},{"pid":"7594ee2820e9aac89f8b9063be5074e1447d49d3","tid":428802,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:29:39.000Z","msg":"霧月夜抱泣落紅， 險些破碎了燈釵夢<br />\n<br />\n別離人對奈何天，離堪怨別堪憐，離心牽柳線，別淚灑花前，甫相逢，才見面<br />\n未見，未見，未見伊人未見，怨天，怨天，怨天空自怨天，望眼將穿，望眼將穿。<br />\n<br />\n一葉輕舟去，人隔萬重山， <br />\n鳥南飛，鳥南返， <br />\n鳥兒比翼何日再歸還，哀我何孤單。<br />\n<br />\n涼風有信，秋月無邊。思嬌情緒好比度日如年。<br />\n<br />\n唉! 冷得我騰~騰~震~<br />\n<br />\n以前啲粵曲填詞幾正幾有味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bfae28e671c2d9db2c417083a1901c895ca89b","tid":428802,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:30:47.000Z","msg":"粵曲先嘈生晒= ="},{"pid":"f31ee85db68aec1ac43577c4af2be93bf63216d8","tid":428802,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>粵曲先嘈生晒= =</blockquote><br />\n某啲係但唔係全部囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3bd15207e59762a9f7fa49ff7d8e51cfb4f0bd","tid":428802,"uid":15863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"屋企有個開到大大聲咁日loop夜loop粵劇嘅老人家就唔係咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘈到爆<br />\n樓上個啲曲聽到識背咁滯"},{"pid":"bd7d78a7ed0bea1481f558ced21d0b4e56f6a034","tid":428802,"uid":49